                    <li>
                        <p><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Ribbon </span>Select <b>Home &gt; Table Properties</b>.  </p>
                    </li>
                    <li><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Right-click</span> Right-click the table and from the context menu, select <span class="Emphasis">Table Properties</span>.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
